2054.subject: HPWE
2054.descrlong: Surveys the rise of experiential education programs and the guiding philosophy of this learning model. Methods of teambuilding and personal development will be practiced in hands-on situations. Requires a weekend backpacking expedition to the Ventana Wilderness. Course fee required. (Offered fall semester.)
